						<b>Korigom-tang (oxtail soup)</b><br><br>
						Oxtail is boiled over a low fire until the meat becomes very tender. The meat is drained, and seasoned with salt, black pepper, diced green onions, garlic, and diluted soy sauce. Then it is put back into the soup and boiled more. 
						</td>
