				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="544">
					<tr valign="top">
						<td width="10" class="o">*</td>
						<td class="o">To eliminate the smell of oxtail, bouquet garni such as bay leaves, basil, and thyme or vegetables such as parsley, celery, carrot, and onions are put in the boiling pot and drained later.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="10" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td class="o">*</td>
						<td class="o">Celery, which is used for eliminating smells, is rich in fiber. It not only eliminates greasy taste but also supplement vitamins and minerals. </td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="20" border="0"></td></tr>
