				<!-- -->
				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="544"> 
					<tr>
						<td colspan="2"><b>Ingredients</b></td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="10" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr>
						<td colspan="2">oxtail 2kg (water 10 L, 3 green onions, 5 garlic cloves), salts, black pepper, chopped green onions</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="10" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td class="o">*</td>
						<td class="o">Meat seasonings: clear soy sauce 1 Tbsp, salt 2 tsp, chopped green onions 2 Tbsp, chopped garlic 1 Tbsp, sesame oil 1 Tbsp, black pepper</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="20" border="0"></td></tr>
				</table>
				
				<!-- -->
				<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="544"> 
					<tr>
						<td colspan="2"><b>Directions</b></td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="10" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td width="15">1)</td>
						<td>Oxtail is sliced to 4~5cm length or if it's a lump, place knife on cartilage between joints and cut. Then, tough outer membrane is removed and meats are put in cold water to remove blood and drained.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>2)</td>
						<td>Oxtails are put in boiling water and boiled on a high fire. Then, reduce the heat and boil 3 more hours. Green onions and garlic are put in the middle of boiling, and fats and bubbles floating on the water are removed.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>3)</td>
						<td>When soup is soaked out and the meat on the tailbone is softened and tender, drain solids and cool the soup and then remove fats on the top.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>4)</td>
						<td>Solids are seasoned with meat seasonings.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>5)</td>
						<td>Soup is reheated and seasoned meat is put in the soup and boil once. Pour soup in a bowl and serve with salt, black pepper, and finely chopped green onions.</td>
					</tr>

